{"id":26314,"date":"2024-02-16T12:39:30","date_gmt":"2021-10-16T07:09:30","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=26314"},"modified":"2023-12-20T18:11:42","modified_gmt":"2023-12-20T12:41:42","slug":"modern-kitchen-design-ideas-with-island","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/modern-kitchen-design-ideas-with-island\/","title":{"rendered":"5 Effortless Modern Kitchen Design Ideas With Island"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Incorporating modern kitchen design ideas with an island for your home isn\u2019t difficult anymore. Here are a few attractive and pocket-friendly ideas that you can choose from<\/span><\/i><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The concept of modern kitchen layouts with islands wasn\u2019t around in Indian homes till a few years ago. It is only now that homeowners are getting influenced by the West and the concept of a <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/kitchen-island-designs-for-home\/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">kitchen island<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> as a part of the house seems trendy. To be sure, it serves as a multifunctional space apart from adding to the aesthetics of the kitchen area.<\/span><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">While some may argue that kitchen islands are perfect for large homes, it isn\u2019t always true. Smaller homes too can accommodate them, provided the kitchen space is designed in a manner that doesn\u2019t make it look packed. Here are a few modern kitchen design ideas with islands that you can opt for and make your home look amazing.<\/span><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A 3-In-1 Kitchen Island For The Nuclear Family<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This is a concept that serves multiple purposes while helping you to save a lot of space. First, this island design serves as a dining space, especially when you have a nuclear family or are just a couple living alone. You do not need a separate <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/dining-room-interiors\/dining-table-designs\/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">dining table<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> when you have this modern kitchen island with seating. Second, the area can be where you prepare for the meals before you start cooking or store cooked food to be consumed later. Third, it serves as a storage space with drawers and cabinets to keep kitchen essentials, crockery, cutlery or anything else that seems suitable to you. With this, your kitchen area looks neat and spacious, with minimal furniture occupying the floor. You can colour the table with a bold hue that is striking.<\/span><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignnone wp-image-26318 size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/16123153\/modern-kitchen-island-with-seating.jpg\" alt=\"Modern kitchen island with seating and cabinet in bold hue that is striking\" class=\"wp-image-26318\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/16123153\/modern-kitchen-island-with-seating.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/16123153\/modern-kitchen-island-with-seating-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/16123153\/modern-kitchen-island-with-seating-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/16123153\/modern-kitchen-island-with-seating-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">This kitchen island is multifunctional and serves as a table, storage space as well as activity area<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">The Busy Kitchen Island To Help Save Space<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">These days, most urban homeowners opt for concealed spaces to fit in their kitchen appliances like the oven, dishwasher, etc. This saves up on floor space where you do not have to use a lot of furniture. Appliances get accommodated alongside cabinets and especially within kitchen islands. The same goes for the sink, where you save space near the cooking area and make room for it in the island. The modern kitchen island with hood and oven allows you to utilise it to the fullest while making it a busy space. You can multitask by using the oven as well as clean up simultaneously. The other side can serve as a seating area to catch up with the other family members while preparing meals. Here too, you can add in a storage space that makes work easy and keeps things hidden.<\/span><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignnone wp-image-26317 size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/16123147\/modern-kitchen-island-with-hood-and-oven.jpg\" alt=\"A modern kitchen island with a hood and oven is a space-saving design and makes work easy\" class=\"wp-image-26317\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/16123147\/modern-kitchen-island-with-hood-and-oven.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/16123147\/modern-kitchen-island-with-hood-and-oven-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/16123147\/modern-kitchen-island-with-hood-and-oven-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/16123147\/modern-kitchen-island-with-hood-and-oven-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">When you have multiple kitchen appliances and need to save space, the kitchen island can hold up a lot of things<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Smart, space saving kitchen solutions for a smooth cooking experience\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/20174913\/smart-space-saving-kitchen-solutions-for-smooth-cooking-experience.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">The Cosy Kitchen Island For Small Spaces<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you are a couple living in a small home and still want an island to adorn the kitchen area, this is just what you need. It is a small island that serves as an activity area to prepare your meals and dining space for both of you. You do not feel the need for an added dining table, and this is what is sufficient. This again can be used as a storage space for kitchen essentials, depending on how you plan to utilise the space below. As a part of modern kitchen island designs with seating, two chairs that fit in well are what you need to make this a perfect addition to your kitchen area.<\/span><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignnone wp-image-26320 size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/16123207\/modern-small-kitchen-design-with-island.jpg\" alt=\"Modern small kitchen design with an island and two chairs are the perfect addition to the kitchen area\" class=\"wp-image-26320\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/16123207\/modern-small-kitchen-design-with-island.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/16123207\/modern-small-kitchen-design-with-island-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/16123207\/modern-small-kitchen-design-with-island-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/16123207\/modern-small-kitchen-design-with-island-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A small and cosy kitchen island not just saves space but also gives a modern touch to your kitchen, especially when the area is diminutive<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">The Marble-Top Kitchen Island For A Sumptuous Look<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Marble has always been associated with luxury as it lends finesse to wherever it is placed. When you put it on your kitchen island, its elegance is what grabs eyeballs. You can opt for wood for the storage space on the walls below the island top and let marble enjoy being on the countertop in the cooking area and the prep area on the island. This gives an appealing look to the modern galley kitchen with island. While maintaining marble may require an added effort, it is all worth it when you clean up well, and your kitchen area looks nice and bright. You can play with lights that bring out the brightness of the marble and make the room look spacious.<\/span><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignnone wp-image-26315 size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/16123134\/modern-galley-kitchen-with-island-marble-top.jpg\" alt=\"Modern galley kitchen with island marble top and seating lends a luxury look\" class=\"wp-image-26315\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/16123134\/modern-galley-kitchen-with-island-marble-top.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/16123134\/modern-galley-kitchen-with-island-marble-top-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/16123134\/modern-galley-kitchen-with-island-marble-top-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/16123134\/modern-galley-kitchen-with-island-marble-top-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Marble-top kitchen islands brighten up the room while making it look elegant. Compliments coming in from guests will become an everyday affair<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Also, check out <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/marble-kitchen-countertops\/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Marble Kitchen Countertops<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">The Granite-Top Kitchen Island For A Busy Family<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">So this can be used when you already have a bright kitchen area due to the wall colours, artificial lights or natural light coming in. Like marble, this is tough and lasts for years. Your kitchen area can be covered with granite, too, while giving it a nice contrast. Granite doesn\u2019t stain that easily, and even if it does, you would barely notice due to the texture. It is easy to clean and helps you with your meal preparation without making a mess. The modern kitchen with centre island again can be used as a dining<\/span><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignnone wp-image-26319 size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/16123201\/modern-kitchen-with-center-island-granite-top.jpg\" alt=\"A modern kitchen with center island granite top and wooden stools gives a classy look\" class=\"wp-image-26319\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/16123201\/modern-kitchen-with-center-island-granite-top.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/16123201\/modern-kitchen-with-center-island-granite-top-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/16123201\/modern-kitchen-with-center-island-granite-top-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/16123201\/modern-kitchen-with-center-island-granite-top-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A granite-top kitchen island lends a classy look and yet allows you to keep things simple. With low maintenance involved, it is perfect for busy families<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">space or a snacking area for kids or for your partner to spend quality time with you while you are whipping up a meal.<\/span><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Kitchen islands serve multiple purposes, and that is the reason why most homes have them. While saving space and adding furniture, it gets to be a perfect addition for modern urban dwellings.<\/span><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Get in touch with experienced designers and experts at <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">DesignCafe<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> today and watch your kitchen area transform like never before.<\/span><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Looking For Modular Kitchens At Best Prices<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Speak to our kitchen experts today!<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- <span class=\"sales-txt-label\" id=\"labeltxt\">Enter your name*<\/span>  -->\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"form-row dc-falg-row\">\n        <!-- <div class=\"form-group col-md-3 guideForm\">\n            <select name=\"your-phone-ext